snippet.title: Terralith 2.0: Overworld Evolved - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Terralith is a datapack that takes Minecraft 1.18's Caves and Cliffs update, and turns it up to eleven. Download Terralith here: https://www.planetminecraft.com/data-pack/terralith-overworld-evolved-100-biomes-caves-and-more/

Terralith adds over 85 biomes, as well as updating almost every vanilla biome with new and improved features. It also includes tons of completely new terrain types - canyons, shattered biomes, floating islands, deep ocean trenches and much, much more. 

Many thanks to Wintertooth100 for his excellent camera work, and Botany for amazing editing.

Music is jiglr - Love Trip! Used with the artist’s permission.
